function Start()

-- If the player got the bonus have the last caster taunt before transforming.
-- If no bonus remove the shield and enable the caster AI.
	if bBonus == true then
		Hydra.ActorPlaySimpleConversation(S_CONVO_CASTER_01, idCultistCaster01)

	elseif Hydra.ActorIsValid(idCultistCaster01) and Hydra.ActorIsAlive(idCultistCaster01) then
		Hydra.ActorPlaySimpleConversation(S_CONVO_FAIL, idCultistCaster01)
		UF_CasterReleased(idCultistCaster01, idShield01)
	end

-- Disable all active spawners. 
	UF_DisableSpawners(tCultistSpawners)
	UF_DisableSpawners(tCultistSummoners)
	
-- Reenable cultist AI.
	local tCultists = Hydra.ActorsInGroup(S_CULTIST_GROUP)

	for i, idCultist in ipairs(tCultists) do
		if Hydra.ActorIsValid(idCultist) then
			Hydra.ActorEnableAI(idCultist, true)
		end
	end
	
-- Enable AI and remove shields for any remaining casters.
	UF_CasterReleased(idCultistCaster02, idShield02)
	UF_CasterReleased(idCultistCaster03, idShield03)

end

function Start(idActor)

-- Get the marker stored on the cultist and ensure the marker is valid.
	local idRunTo = Hydra.GetActorVariable(idActor, "N_MARKER_RUNTO")
	if Hydra.ActorIsValid(idRunTo) then
	
	-- Get the actors position vs the marker it's running toward with a little leeway.	
		local N_POSITION_RANGE = 0.1
		local N_POSITION_RANGE_SQ = math.pow(N_POSITION_RANGE, 2)
		local nActorVsMarkerPosition = Hydra.ActorDistanceSquaredBetweenActors(idActor, idRunTo)
		
	-- Get the actors facing angle vs it's marker with a little leeway.	
		local nActorFacing = Hydra.ActorGetFacing(idActor)
		local nMarkerFacing = Hydra.ActorGetFacing(idRunTo)
		local N_FACING_RANGE = 0.1
		local nActorVsMarkerAngle = Hydra.FacingGetAngleBetween(nActorFacing, nMarkerFacing)
		
	-- If the cultist has reached the marker location and is facing it correctly then start the transform power.
	-- If the cultist is CC'd this will cause them to continue to the marker before transforming.
		if bEventStarted == true then 
			if nActorVsMarkerPosition <= N_POSITION_RANGE and nActorVsMarkerAngle <= N_FACING_RANGE then
				Hydra.QActorWait(idActor, 0.1)
				Hydra.QActorAnimAndNewIdle(idActor, S_CULTIST_KNEEL_INTRO, S_CULTIST_KNEEL)
				Hydra.QActorPower(idActor, S_CULTIST_TRANSFORM, idActor)
				Hydra.ActorDelete(idRunTo)
			else 
				Hydra.QActorMoveToLocationDynamicSpeed(idActor, idRunTo, "NPC_RUN", true)
				Hydra.QActorFaceSameAsActor(idActor, idRunTo)
			end
		end

	end

end

function Start(idActorSpawned, idActorSpawner)

-- Dropping a marker on the spawner for each cultist.
-- Setting cultists to run to the marker and face the center.
-- (The ability to target the spawners themselves is not functioning).

	local idRunTo = Hydra.ActorSpawnActor(S_MARKER, idActorSpawner, false, 0,0)

	Hydra.QActorMoveToLocationDynamicSpeed(idActorSpawned, idRunTo, "NPC_RUN", true)
	Hydra.QActorFaceSameAsActor(idActorSpawned, idRunTo)	

-- Disabling the cultist AI
	Hydra.ActorEnableAI(idActorSpawned, false) 
	
-- Storing the dropped marker to be deleted in Phase 2 AIQueue Empty.
	Hydra.SetActorVariable(idActorSpawned, "N_MARKER_RUNTO", idRunTo)
	
end

--------------------------------
-- Enable spawners in a table --
function UF_EnableSpawners(tSpawners)

	for i, idSpawner in ipairs(tSpawners) do
		if Hydra.ActorIsValid(idSpawner) then
			Hydra.ActorGizmoSetDisabled(idSpawner,false)
		end
	end
	
end

---------------------------------
-- Disable spawners in a table --
function UF_DisableSpawners(tSpawners)

	for i, idSpawner in ipairs(tSpawners) do
		if Hydra.ActorIsValid(idSpawner) then
			Hydra.ActorGizmoSetDisabled(idSpawner,true)
		end
	end
	
end

------------------------------------
-- Turn casters into elite demons --
function UF_CasterTransform(idCaster, idShield)

	if Hydra.ActorIsValid(idCaster) and Hydra.ActorIsAlive(idCaster) then
		Hydra.BuffApplyToTarget(S_CULTIST_CASTER_TRANSFORM, "TRANSFORM", idCaster)
	end	
	
-- Delete the shield
	if Hydra.ActorIsValid(idShield) then
		Hydra.ActorDelete(idShield)
	end	
	
end

--------------------------------------------------------------------------------
-- Mastery failed, turn on caster AI and remove invulnerablity and shield vfx --
function UF_CasterReleased(idCaster, idShield)
	
	if Hydra.ActorIsValid(idCaster) and Hydra.ActorIsAlive(idCaster) then
		Hydra.ActorEnableAI(idCaster, true)
		Hydra.ActorSetInvulnerable(idCaster, false)
		Hydra.BuffRemove(S_GENERIC_IMMUNE, "IMMUNE", idCaster)
	end
	
-- Delete the shield
	if Hydra.ActorIsValid(idShield) then
		Hydra.ActorDelete(idShield)
	end	
	
end
